column8: Partly cloudy. Winds southeasterly 25 to 40 km/h.
Cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers in the late morning and afternoon. Winds southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light in the late evening.

Partly cloudy. Patchy morning fog in the northeast suburbs. Medium (40%) chance of showers in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and early evening, mainly over the eastern suburbs. Winds southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending southerly 15 to 25 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.

Partly cloudy. Areas of morning fog. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Light winds becoming southerly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. Light winds becoming southerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds south to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h.
Cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Winds south to southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h.
